Please run the below commands to install PortAudio as mentioned in packages.txt (if you don't already have it installed)

1. git clone https://github.com/PortAudio/portaudio.git\
2. cd portaudio\
3. mkdir build\
4. cd build\
5. cmake ..\
6. make -j$(sysctl -n hw.logicalcpu)\
7. sudo make install

** The above commands will install PortAudio in your system **


Next use pip/conda to install the dependencies given in requirements.txt file

Command:
pip install -r requirements.txt
